# AstroGuard MAS — Environment Variables
# Paste your actual NASA API key below (received via email from api.nasa.gov)

# NASA NeoWs API Key (Near Earth Object Web Service)
# Endpoints used:
#   - Neo Feed:   GET https://api.nasa.gov/neo/rest/v1/feed?start_date=YYYY-MM-DD&end_date=YYYY-MM-DD&api_key=KEY
#   - Neo Lookup: GET https://api.nasa.gov/neo/rest/v1/neo/{asteroid_id}?api_key=KEY
#   - Neo Browse: GET https://api.nasa.gov/neo/rest/v1/neo/browse?api_key=KEY
# Get your free key at: https://api.nasa.gov/
NASA_API_KEY=PASTE_YOUR_KEY_HERE